{# CONTENT SECTION #}
<section class="relative bg-white px-4 md:px-6 py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16">

      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">Why this guide exists</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            <strong>56% of Nepali industries</strong> cite lack of skilled manpower as the primary barrier to AI adoption. This isn't a technology problem. It's a knowledge problem. Businesses in Kathmandu and across Nepal know AI can help them compete, but they don't know where to start.
          </p>
          <p class="text-warm-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This guide bridges that gap. We provide practical, budget-conscious implementation strategies tailored for Nepal's market conditions. Whether you're a 10-person startup or a 500-person enterprise, you'll find a path forward.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">Budget tiers for Nepal</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-green-500">
              <p class="text-xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">NPR 50,000 - 200,000</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600 mb-2"><strong>Starter tier:</strong> AI chatbots, basic automation</p>
              <p class="text-warm-500 text-sm">Best for: Customer service automation, FAQ bots, simple data processing. Uses cloud APIs with minimal custom development.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
              <p class="text-xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">NPR 500,000 - 2,000,000</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600 mb-2"><strong>Growth tier:</strong> Custom AI solutions, integrations</p>
              <p class="text-warm-500 text-sm">Best for: AI search, document processing, recommendation systems. Includes custom model training and system integration.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
              <p class="text-xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">NPR 5,000,000+</p>
              <p class="text-warm-600 mb-2"><strong>Enterprise tier:</strong> Full AI transformation</p>
              <p class="text-warm-500 text-sm">Best for: End-to-end AI platforms, predictive analytics, autonomous operations. Includes dedicated infrastructure and ongoing optimization.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-4">What you get:</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {% for item in resource.whatYouGet %}
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-zunkiree-600 mt-1">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">{{ item }}</span>
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-10" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-warm-black mb-6">Frequently asked questions</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">Do we need to hire AI specialists?</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Not necessarily. At the starter tier, you can implement AI using cloud APIs with existing developers. Growth tier projects benefit from AI consultants. Enterprise tier typically requires dedicated ML engineers, though you can partner with firms like Zunkiree Labs.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">What about data privacy regulations in Nepal?</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-600">Nepal's data protection framework is evolving. This guide covers current NTA regulations and best practices for data handling. We recommend local data storage for sensitive applications and provide compliance checklists.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-warm-black mb-2">Should we build or buy AI solutions?</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-600">The guide includes a detailed decision framework. In general: buy for standard use cases (chatbots, search), build for competitive differentiation, and partner for complex implementations where you lack in-house expertise.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5" data-reveal>
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          {% set formTitle = resource.formTitle %}
          {% set ctaText = resource.ctaText %}
          {% include "components/lead-capture-form.njk" %}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script type="application/ld+json">
